# Typing Speed Tester (C)

A console-based typing speed tester written in C.  
The program measures typing speed (WPM) and accuracy by comparing user input with predefined sentences.

## Features

- Random sentence selection
- Countdown before typing begins
- Words Per Minute (WPM) calculation
- Accuracy percentage calculation
- Multiple rounds with average results

## Demo

Example output:

=== Advanced Typing Speed Test ===

Round 1/3  
Type this sentence:  
The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.

Time: 8.23 sec  
WPM: 56  
Accuracy: 97.4%

## How It Works

1. User selects number of rounds.
2. Program randomly selects a sentence.
3. Timer starts when the user begins typing.
4. Program calculates:
   - Words Per Minute
   - Accuracy
   - Average score after all rounds.

